(80, 1, '2015-03-20 22:27:10', '2015-03-20 22:27:10', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-xs-12">\r\n<div id="tabs">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="#tabs-1">CONSULTANCY &amp; <br>PLANNING</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#tabs-2">SERVICE &amp; <br>REPAIRS</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#tabs-3">EQUIPMENT PREVENTIVE<br> MAINTENANCE</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#tabs-4">CUSTOMISED STAINLESS <br>STELL FABRICATION</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div id="tabs-1">\r\n\r\nWe provide consultation to design and create an efficient kitchen for our clients. Our team of professionals would advise you on the appropriate equipment selection and provide the kitchen layout to ensure that the equipment are well placed in the kitchen.\r\nIn addition, our experienced kitchen designers would also provide the mechanical, electrical (M&E) and plumbing services drawings to your contractor to facilitate the smooth coordination and completion of project.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="tabs-2">\r\n\r\nWe have a team of trained and skilled technicians to provide the servicing and repairs of equipment should it encounter any electrical, mechanical or plumbing fault and has become out of order or broken.\r\nWe are also able to provide a wide range of spare parts to replace faulty components and return essential equipment back to working condition.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="tabs-3">\r\n\r\nWe offer equipment preventive maintenance services to provide systematic inspection, detection, and correction of incipient failures either before they occur or before they develop into major defects.\r\nIn addition, our trained technicians would record equipment deterioration and provide recommendation to our clients to replace or repair worn parts before they cause system failure. The ideal preventive maintenance program would prevent all equipment failure before it occurs.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="tabs-4">\r\n\r\nThe design and customisation of stainless steel equipment such as worktables, washing sinks, wall shelving and storage racks are fundamental to complement the operational efficiency of every kitchen.\r\nWe have experienced product designers who can design customised fabrication according to your requirements. We ensure that the quality stainless steel equipment would fit seamlessly and fittingly in your kitchen and galleys.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-9">\r\n<h3 class="thank">Thank you for Choosing Universal Steel</h3>\r\nWe will try to give you the satisfaction you had more and Better services.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 services-rightimg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-606" src="http://localhost/universal-beta/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-img.jpg" alt="services-img" width="259" height="195" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-12 applyservices">\r\n<h2>How to Apply the service call</h2>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<div class="checkname">\r\n<h4>Check your model name &amp; Serial Number</h4>\r\n<img src="http://localhost/universal-beta/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/check-name.jpg" alt="check-name" width="150" height="137" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-1 services-arrow"><img src="http://localhost/universal-beta/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/servicespage-arrow.png" alt="servicespage-arrow" width="143" height="69" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<div class="callus">\r\n<h4>Call us like below</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service Hotline : 6280-7333</li>\r\n	<li>[During Operation Hour]</li>\r\n	<li>Service Hotline : 8322-0855</li>\r\n	<li>[After Operation Hour]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-611 size-full" src="http://localhost/universal-beta/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/callus-icon.jpg" alt="callus-icon" width="114" height="114" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-1 services-arrow"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-610" src="http://localhost/universal-beta/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/servicespage-arrow.png" alt="ser