(130, 1, '2015-05-20 06:03:20', '2015-05-20 06:03:20', '<div class="row">\n<div class="col-xs-8">\n<div id="tabs">\n<ul>\n	<li><a href="#tabs-1">ABOUT US</a></li>\n	<li><a href="#tabs-2">VISION</a></li>\n	<li><a href="#tabs-3">MISSION</a></li>\n	<li><a href="#tabs-4">VALUES</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div id="tabs-1">\n\n<span style="color: #339fd3;">UNIVERSAL STEEL INDURSTRIES PTE LTD</span> was established in 1993, we are leading company in Singapore specialized in Food Service equipment.\n\n</div>\n<div id="tabs-2">\n\nTo become top company in the Food Service Industries.\n\n</div>\n<div id="tabs-3">\n\nTo satisfy every clients need by providing professional solution.\n\n</div>\n<div id="tabs-4">\n\n<span style="color: #339fd3;">Commitment</span> -&gt; Assuring quality service to all our clients.\n<span style="color: #339fd3;">Responsibility</span> -&gt; Assuring quality support &amp; After sales service.\n<span style="color: #339fd3;">Relationship</span> -&gt; Assuring development of closer relationship with all our business partners.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-xs-4"><a href="http://universalsteel.exhibitmedia.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-914" src="http://universalsteel.exhibitmedia.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img-300x296.jpg" alt="aboutus-img" width="300" height="296" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<!--\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>(</b><span style="color: #ff0000;"><b>U</b></span><b>NIVERSAL </b><span style="color: #ff0000;"><b>S</b></span><b>TEEL </b><span style="color: #ff0000;"><b>I</b></span><b>NDURSTRIES PTE LTD.)</b> was established in 1993, we are leading company in Singapore specialized in Food Service equipment.\n<div><span style="color: #ff0000;"><b><a href="http://192.168.1.4/universalsteel/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img1.jpg"><img class=" size-full wp-image-241 alignleft" src="http://192.168.1.4/universalsteel/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img1.jpg" alt="aboutus-img1" width="64" height="66" /></a>U</b></span><b>nited workforce to create positive result.</b></div>\n<div><span style="color: #ff0000;"><b><a href="http://192.168.1.4/universalsteel/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img2.jpg"><img class=" size-full wp-image-242 alignleft" src="http://192.168.1.4/universalsteel/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img2.jpg" alt="aboutus-img2" width="64" height="66" /></a>S</b></span><b>pirit to accept negative comments for future improvement.</b></div>\n<div><span style="color: #ff0000;"><b><a href="http://192.168.1.4/universalsteel/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img3.jpg"><img class=" size-full wp-image-243 alignleft" src="http://192.168.1.4/universalsteel/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/aboutus-img3.jpg" alt="aboutus-img3" width="64" height="66" /></a>I</b></span><b>nnovative ideas to provide efficient solution.</b></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\nWe concentrate in developing complete projects big or small based on client requirements and effect their execution from design through operational full kitchen with all facilities while offering complete, efficient, and rapid after sales service.\n\n<strong>\nThe Most Professional Company</strong>\nWe Universal Steel Industries Pte Ltd, coupled with experienced people, and the latest technology of the complete product ranges available today, provides each and every customer with planning, design, estimation, equipment, procurement, installation, user training, maintenance and technical support (Service &amp; Parts).\n\nWe are a very professional organization and is therefore; in the position to give professional advice on the choice of the most appropriate equipment to best meet specific requirement. Its size and experience gathered over many years of work, surely makes us competent and totally reliable partner for its customers. We have a leading position which is confirmed by the market share achieved by the company.\n\nWe offers a full line of equipment for the preparation, cooking, exhaust systems, specialized cooking, conservation, distribution of food, refrigeration, Commercial Shelving, dish handling, dry stores. It is due to our careful, constant, continued organization, and technological development that we are equipped to meet customer''s ever-changing demands.-->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-20 06:03:20', '2015-05-20 06:03:20', '', 9, 'http://localhost/universalsteel/9-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
