rmed by the market share achieved by the company.\r\n\r\nWe offers a full line of equipment for the preparation, cooking, exhaust systems, specialized cooking, conservation, distribution of food, refrigeration, Commercial Shelving, dish handling, dry stores. It is due to our careful, constant, continued organization, and technological development that we are equipped to meet customer''s ever-changing demands.-->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-20 07:10:32', '2015-05-20 07:10:32', '', 9, 'http://universalsteel.exhibitmedia.sg/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
